This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic sentence embeddings. The use of deep latent variable models and transformers also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the mention of data generating distributions and inference networks suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision) which deals with image and video processing.
